Use pnpm "onlyBuiltDependencies" for common libs in package.json, for example:

```
  "pnpm": {
    "onlyBuiltDependencies": [
      "better-sqlite3",
      "esbuild",
      "sqlite3"
    ],
    "peerDependencyRules": {
      "allowedVersions": {
        "@types/node": ">=16"
      }
    }
  }
```
